1. Enter the option number (1, 2, or 3).
2. When the program asks "(1/2) Enter Message: ", enter a no space message. The program is case insensitive.
3. When the program asks "((2/2) Enter Key: )", enter a no space key. The program is case insensitive.
4. The program will print the result into the terminal for option 1 and 2.
5. The program is on a loop until option 3 is selected.
6. Selecting option 3 will terminate the program.